Package com.binance4j.staking.dto

Record Class ProductPosition

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
com.binance4j.staking.dto.ProductPosition
Record Components:
positionId - Staking position ID.
productId - Staking project ID.
asset - Locked asset.
amount - Locked Amount.
purchaseTime - Subscription time.
duration - Lock period(days ).
accrualDays - Accrue days.
rewardAsset - Earned asset.
apy - APY.
rewardAmt - Earned amount.
extraRewardAsset - Rewards assets of extra staking type.
extraRewardAPY - APY of extra staking type.
estExtraRewardAmt - Rewards of extra staking type, distribute when order expires.
nextInterestPay - Next estimated interest payment.
nextInterestPayDate - Next interest payment date.
payInterestPeriod - Interest cycle.
redeemAmountEarly - Early redemption amount.
interestEndDate - Interest accrual end date.
deliverDate - Redemption arrival time.
redeemPeriod - Redemption interval.
redeemingAmt - Amount under redemption.
partialAmtDeliverDate - Arrival time of partial redemption amount of order.
canRedeemEarly - When it is true, early redemption can be operated.
renewable - When it is true, auto staking can be operated.
type - Order type is auto-staking or normal.
status - Position status.
public record ProductPosition(String positionId, String productId, String asset, String amount, String purchaseTime, String duration, String accrualDays, String rewardAsset, String apy, String rewardAmt, String extraRewardAsset, String extraRewardAPY, String estExtraRewardAmt, String nextInterestPay, String nextInterestPayDate, String payInterestPeriod, String redeemAmountEarly, String interestEndDate, String deliverDate, String redeemPeriod, String redeemingAmt, String partialAmtDeliverDate, boolean canRedeemEarly, boolean renewable, String type, String status) extends Record
Product position.
